The girls we sent out last night to drink with our customers.

52
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,899
We are just bringing them back.

53
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:40,770
- Are there any newcomers?
- Yes.

54
00:04:40,770 --> 00:04:43,270
- Let me take a look.
- Go ahead.

55
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:49,319
General Zhou, do you still remember me?

56
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:51,720
I really miss you.

57
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:55,850
Yes, your name is Cuixiang.

58
00:04:55,850 --> 00:04:58,790
Move yourself. Let me take a look at the newcomers.

59
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:02,590
Give me a smile.

60
00:05:03,370 --> 00:05:04,870
Great.

61
00:05:10,980 --> 00:05:12,880
Sit tight.

62
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:14,310
Go.

63
00:05:15,790 --> 00:05:18,330
General Zhou, you are welcome to visit us.

64
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:26,460
Thanks, girls.

65
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:29,080
You are welcome, Mr. Jing.

66
00:05:50,140 --> 00:05:52,550
General Zhou, nothing suspicious.

67
00:06:03,290 --> 00:06:05,140
What are these?

68
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:09,640
Sir, these are fresh foods for Guangtai House. It's a long trip.

69
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:12,429
To keep the foods fresh, we use ice to keep them cold.

70
00:06:12,429 --> 00:06:16,240
You just saw it. We prepared ice cubes for this trip.

71
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:21,490
Zhenyuan Escort even started to deliver fresh foods.

72
00:06:23,010 --> 00:06:24,899
It's a difficult time to make a living now.

73
00:06:24,899 --> 00:06:27,740
We are glad that our old clients hired us.

74
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:33,999
Thank you for guarding the city.

75
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,400
Have a drink and relax yourself when you have time.

76
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,830
Go.

77
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:39,409
- Thank you, Sir.
- Hurry up.

78
00:06:39,409 --> 00:06:40,900
Go.

79
